        "rich_text_rEPGfU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "From Bold to Timeless",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>From Bold to Timeless</h2><p>While 2024 embraced bold individuality with asymmetry, vibrant gemstones and eclectic metal mixing, 2025 refined this approach, leaning into understated elegance with quiet luxury, delicate jewelry and minimalism. The maximalist energy marked by artistic asymmetry and cultural fusion, evolves into a more polished aesthetic, where timeless classics like pearls and vintage-inspired designs take centre stage.</p>",
            "custom_id": "frombold",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
