        "image_with_text_CLzYQk": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Delicate Jewelry: Subtle Yet Striking",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/A_Glimpse_into_the_Future_of_Fashion_1st_Image_600_x_500.jpg",
            "text": "<h2>Delicate Jewelry: Subtle Yet Striking</h2><p>In 2025, delicate jewelry is set to become the top choice for those who value subtle elegance. Think minimalistic chains, fine <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-rings\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Rings\">rings</a> and small, delicate <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-earrings\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Earrings\">earrings</a>. These pieces allow for versatility, whether worn alone or layered for a more personalized style. Expected to be a must-have in every jewelry collection, they offer sophistication without overpowering your style. Perfect for everyday wear, these understated pieces will remain at the forefront of this year’s jewelry trends.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "delicate",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_4hByhi": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Mixed Metal Jewelry: Breaking Boundaries",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/A_Glimpse_into_the_Future_of_Fashion_2nd_Image_600_x_500.jpg",
            "text": "<h2>Mixed Metal Jewelry: Breaking Boundaries</h2><p>The days of wearing just one metal are over. Mixed metal jewelry will take centre stage, allowing women to blend different tones in unique and eye-catching designs. This trend encourages creativity, offering a modern twist on classic jewelry styles. Whether it’s rings, <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-bracelets\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Bracelets\">bracelets</a> or earrings, combining various metals adds depth and character to any piece, making it an exciting trend for those who love to experiment with their jewelry.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "mixedmetal",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_YkgwV3": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Layering Jewelry: Bold and Beautiful",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/A_Glimpse_into_the_Future_of_Fashion_3rd_Image_600_x_500.jpg",
            "text": "<h2>Layering Jewelry: Bold and Beautiful</h2><p>Layering jewelry remains a standout trend in 2025, with stacking rings and layering <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-necklaces\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Necklace\">necklaces</a> becoming the go-to way to express personal style. This trend empowers women to mix and match different styles, textures, and lengths, the possibilities for creativity being endless. The key to mastering the layered look lies in balancing bold statement pieces with delicate accents, creating a look that's both vibrant and effortlessly cohesive.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "layering",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_QiNPnR": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Quiet Luxury: Understated Wealth",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/A_Glimpse_into_the_Future_of_Fashion_4th_Image_600_x_500.jpg",
            "text": "<h2>Quiet Luxury: Understated Wealth</h2><p>Quiet luxury is all about elegance without overt displays of wealth. In 2025, Indian women will lean towards jewelry that exudes luxury through its refined craftsmanship and subtle charm. This trend is about investing in timeless pieces, without the need for flashy motifs or extravagant designs. Think premium gold, delicate diamonds and intricate detailing that speak to the wearer’s refined taste and appreciation for understated wealth.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "quietluxury",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_PmQ7Kf": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Minimalism: Less is More",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/A_Glimpse_into_the_Future_of_Fashion_5th_Image_600_x_500.jpg",
            "text": "<h2>Minimalism: Less is More</h2><p>Minimalism will continue to rule the jewelry scenes, celebrating clean lines, sleek designs and a refined approach to accessorizing. Characterized by thin bands, small studs and simple chains, the concept embodies timeless appeal that dominates the market. These pieces offer versatility, easily transitioning from casual daywear to elegant evening looks, making them a staple in any collection. Ideal for those who appreciate a subtle yet striking style, it enhances your look without ever overshadowing it.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "minimalism",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_jyDw3E": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Old Money Jewelry: Nostalgic Elegance",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/A_Glimpse_into_the_Future_of_Fashion_6th_Image_600_x_500.jpg",
            "text": "<h2>Old Money Jewelry: Nostalgic Elegance</h2><p>Vintage-inspired or “old-money” jewelry is making a notable comeback this year. This trend embraces the timeless elegance of bygone eras, featuring designs that exude a sense of sophistication and wealth. Picture classic gold pieces, statement necklaces and intricately crafted rings that carry the charm of heirlooms passed down through generations. This revival is all about investing in exceptional craftsmanship, lasting quality and enduring beauty, pieces that transcend trends, and always make a statement of refinement and grace.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "oldmoney",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_QLU38d": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Embrace the Trends",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Embrace the Trends: Curate Your Signature Jewelry Collection Today!</h2><p>The jewelry trends of 2025 are here and it's time for you to find the pieces that will define your style for the year ahead. Whether you’re drawn to delicate designs, bold layering or timeless old-school elegance, there’s something for everyone. Don’t just follow trends - set them! Head to our jewelry collection and choose the perfect pieces that reflect your unique fashion sense.</p>",
            "custom_id": "curate",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
